The Postmaster of Mafdet maintains a standing commission for a complete route survey of the Eastern Desert. The desert's full extent has never been formally documented, and outbound expeditions from Mafdet operating in the Eastern Desert have relied on partial and inconsistent records. Survey every accessible section and return with a complete navigation record.
Your Eastern Desert survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority reference office. The postmaster has closed the commission and the route record is now the primary navigation reference for expeditions departing Mafdet into the Eastern Desert.

